description: Hey folks of Philly, you’ll be feelin’ the love for the scrumptious Asian Fusion food that this truck is wheelin’. Their menu mixes Chinese, Japanese, and Thai influences, resulting in an exciting selection of Rice Balls, Sushi Bombs, Popcorn Chicken, Noodle Soups, and so much more. Don’t forget to order their Thai Tea, as it’s of the highest quali-tea. With fantastic food at fantastic prices, they’re successfully serving everything you could ever wish for. After such a great meal, you’ll agree that this truck is wheely, wheely good. Really, really!
name: Wheely Wheely Good
